  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for samba",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for samba fixes the following issues\n\n- CVE-2026-2340: vfs_worm does not block directory modification (bsc#1261158).\n- CVE-2026-3238: unauthenticated udp packet crashes AD DC nbt server (bsc#1261160).\n- CVE-2026-4408: Remote Code Execution in SAMR (bsc#1261163).\n- CVE-2026-4480: Unauthenticated Remote Code Execution (bsc#1261161).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
